This is a modified version of ibus-cloud-pinyin project on http://code.google.com/p/ibus-cloud-pinyin/

My popuse is to update code for vala 0.12 on Ubuntu, for easier compile & install.

INSTALL on Ubuntu (tested in 11.04):
  apt-get install liblua5.1-0-dev liblua5.1-socket2 libsqlite3-dev libibus-dev libnotify-dev lua5.1 libgee-dev valac sqlite3
  git clone git://github.com/liruqi/ibus-cloud-pinyin.git
  cd ibus-cloud-pinyin
  make
  sudo make install

